Package: kluster
Title: A package for scalable approximation of the number of clusters 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hossein Estiri, Aboozar Hadavand [aut, cre] 
Maintainer: Hossein Estiri <estiri.hossein@gmail.com>, Aboozar Hadavand <hadavand.a@gmail.com>
Description: The package deploys a procedure on the model-based approach using approximate Bayes factor for cluster number approximation. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: i2b2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr
Imports: dplyr, DBI, tidytext, ggplot2, reshape2, reshape, purrr, plyr, stringr, mclust, clusterGeneration,tictoc
BugReports: https://github.com/hestiri/kluster/issues
